## Disclaimer
Please note that this free WHMCS plugin is offered without any support from croit.
Unfortunately, our technical support cannot offer WHMCS support.
Furthermore, you should customize this plugin to your needs and check it before use.

## Installation Instructions

1.Upload (calculate_uploaded.php)  file into your (WHMCS rootdirectory/crons/).

2.Upload (croit folder (all files in this folder)) into your (WHMCS rootdirectory/modules/servers/).

3.Login to WHMCS admin ->products/services ->click on create new group ->create product group name  ->save changes. 

4.Click on create product ->create new product ->Product Type ->Product Group(your product group)-> Module(croit)->Continue.

5.Click on tab Module setting -> select your module(croit) ->configure it.

